{"tid":335810,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"記得以前一有咩差嘅政策之類 高登會洗晒板係咁討論","createTime":"2017-07-26T01:37:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-02T07:22:49.000Z","uid":20736,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2b1b2601939cdad10d8e63d19b497d01ff0c3b67","tid":335810,"uid":20736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T01:37:40.000Z","msg":"以前真係發現好多人關注<br />\n好多人討論<br />\n入面亦唔係講咩不了 要返工 呢啲磨滅士氣嘅說話<br />\n到底係因為連登限制左每個台淨係得三個上到熱門<br />\n呢次件事咁大都仲見唔到有咩迴響<br />\n連登已經算比較自由 多港派嘅一個群體<br />\n連呢到嘅反對聲音都咁細嘅話...<br />\n就算唔多識政治野 起碼去關注下留意下啦"},{"pid":"fcd24eef752262a47c2100ebee8265931155ce32","tid":335810,"uid":24836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T01:38:38.000Z","msg":"一地兩檢。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"aa61409314b56e945d2c88599fddeed0ff6a4afd","tid":335810,"uid":20736,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T01:39:59.000Z","msg":"連呢到啲反應都咁淡<br />\n無救了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dcbe54bd8547336a75c4db29cc755644353ada3","tid":335810,"uid":55598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T01:43:17.000Z","msg":"都係中意一個時事台既時候<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac204420290af2fb090ddc613d5474fc30181aad","tid":335810,"uid":33635,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T01:45:32.000Z","msg":"我都好有同感<br />\n以前呢啲事 根本成個高登都會係講緊呢樣嘢<br />\n而家連登想揾下啲人討論都要突登入時事台揾<br />\n應該係話而家啲人由雨革失敗到DQ 開始越嚟越有無力感<br />\n個個都覺得自己改變唔到<br />\n再加上大量真假難分嘅淡友係到不了 而家只會越嚟越少人理"},{"pid":"f4605bfce2ac3d30e60f01dd88fa26118744a080","tid":335810,"uid":24836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T01:46:09.000Z","msg":"怨唔到。。<br />\n一睇到d 為錢去七一上街班後生。 唔知想點"},{"pid":"7ed815397ca170fe00f89f696b116e57b281873e","tid":335810,"uid":44461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T01:48:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>連呢到啲反應都咁淡<br />\n無救了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n想問呢句廢話同不了要返工嘅分別係?"},{"pid":"5bbf7c0af2d7a54fadbe657fc7e41dd09e0ba3f0","tid":335810,"uid":20736,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T01:50:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都好有同感<br />\n以前呢啲事 根本成個高登都會係講緊呢樣嘢<br />\n而家連登想揾下啲人討論都要突登入時事台揾<br />\n應該係話而家啲人由雨革失敗到DQ 開始越嚟越有無力感<br />\n個個都覺得自己改變唔到<br />\n再加上大量真假難分嘅淡友係到不了 而家只會越嚟越少人理</blockquote><br />\n仲有啲人成日講埋晒啲咩 不了要返工 快啲移民<br />\n成日講民啲磨滅意志嘅說話真係好打擊士氣同洗腦<br />\n頭先入左個po有人話講呢堆個啲都係block過嘅人<br />\n我唔知真定假 但我都覺講呢啲野嘅人好鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cefacd6d0e9716893f6d31fdc2043f78d6892511","tid":335810,"uid":20736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T01:51:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>連呢到啲反應都咁淡<br />\n無救了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n想問呢句廢話同不了要返工嘅分別係?</blockquote><br />\n啱 sor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16503828d15ec746e0d67329ba04cbe05eb4a06e","tid":335810,"uid":514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T01:57:22.000Z","msg":"好多五毛扮淡友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cede35003cc1a40e603541f49188afd768f59533","tid":335810,"uid":44461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T01:57:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>連呢到啲反應都咁淡<br />\n無救了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n想問呢句廢話同不了要返工嘅分別係?</blockquote><br />\n啱 sor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係想怪你，不過我都好明白你嘅心情<br />\n即管做引起多啲回響，fb又好身邊人又好，灰心都唔係辦法"},{"pid":"93f5d796dbe646bcd617768618cca659b7440529","tid":335810,"uid":31384,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T02:05:28.000Z","msg":"老實講<br />\n我唔覺得呢度會有人肯真真正正認真討論<br />\n講多兩講又起晒槓<br />\n最後又係五毛港豬互屌"},{"pid":"94d39c9c89cb408b34196db4ee97867857d6556c","tid":335810,"uid":13173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T07:22:49.000Z","msg":"宜家啲無聊/恥笑posts d 正評竟然仲多個啲認真討論/決策posts<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}